Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.23,0:19:04.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Papa!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.66,0:19:03.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,パパ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.01,0:19:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yumi... {\alpha&HFF&}Eriko?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.18,0:19:07.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,由美、恵利子…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.40,0:19:07.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yumi... Eriko?
