Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.77,0:19:09.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何してるのよ、こんなところで…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.82,0:19:12.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,帰ってくるならちゃんと言ってよね
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.82,0:19:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're going to come home, just say so. {\alpha&HFF&}I haven't bought you any dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.08,0:19:15.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あなたの分のおかず、買ってないわよ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.16,0:19:16.05,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're going to come home, just say so. I haven't bought you any dinner.
