Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.58,0:19:37.16,Default,,0,0,0,,That means we can come to this park... {\alpha&HFF&}even the zoo... or theme parks...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.16,0:19:40.86,Default,,0,0,0,,That means we can come to this park... even the zoo... {\alpha&HFF&}or theme parks...
